title: Nordic Baltic Security – Perspectives from the US, UK and the North
arranger: Axel och Margaret Ax:son Johnsons stiftelse, The Changing Character of War Programme, Oxford University
description: What will the Trump presidency mean for security in the Nordic Baltic region? In this seminar, leading security experts from the US, the UK and the Nordic countries will discuss the history of co-operation in the region as well as recent developments and the road ahead.
